and the next one after.

1566
02:01:23,904 --> 02:01:25,671
<i>And for whatever there is</i>

1567
02:01:25,673 --> 02:01:27,906
<i>on the road
that follows from here,</i>

1568
02:01:27,908 --> 02:01:30,742
