1582
02:02:20,095 --> 02:02:23,364
- <i>and are welcome.</i>
- You have a lovely dinner.

1583
02:02:23,366 --> 02:02:26,100
<i>And we have large gatherings</i>

1584
02:02:26,102 --> 02:02:31,406
