1586
02:02:39,216 --> 02:02:43,718
<i>I am older,
and I see things differently,</i>

1587
02:02:43,720 --> 02:02:46,591
<i>and I finally understand you.</i>

1588
02:02:51,894 --> 02:02:55,831
<i>And I take care
of your dresses.</i>

1589
02:02:55,833 --> 02:02:58,701
<i>Keeping them from dust and...</i>

1590
